imdb.plot outline: It's sushi's night. Time has come for Genie and Estelle to speak about their week. When everything seems wrong in your life, should you just wait for the storm to pass or should you act? Génie and Estelle decide to go on a road trip to escape their life. Come and join them to their journey.
